00:07:01.549 --> 00:07:03.606
We've also seen a titillation strategy

00:07:03.606 --> 00:07:05.543
where males are actually

00:07:05.543 --> 00:07:07.691
pleasing their female partners into choosing them

00:07:07.691 --> 00:07:09.410
as a sex partner.

00:07:09.410 --> 00:07:11.855
Now unfortunately, in the animal kingdom,

00:07:11.855 --> 00:07:14.271
