00:07:14.271 --> 00:07:16.010
time and time again.

00:07:16.010 --> 00:07:18.357
It's very common in many phyla,

00:07:18.357 --> 00:07:20.990
from invertebrates to avian species,

00:07:20.990 --> 00:07:23.536
mammals, and, of course, even in primates.

00:07:23.536 --> 00:07:27.073
Now interestingly, there 
